# Java / Spring

- **Lombok** for boilerplate (`@Data`, `@Builder`, `@RequiredArgsConstructor`) — no hand-written getters/setters
- **Constructor injection** only (not `@Autowired` on fields)
- **Tests:** `@WebMvcTest` + `@MockitoBean` (Spring Boot 4 — not deprecated `@MockBean`)
- Fishing endpoints call **USGS + NWS** — can take several seconds; do not assume sub-second responses
- No DB by default (`DataSourceAutoConfiguration` excluded in `application.yaml`)
- CORS allows `localhost:3000`, `caseycapozzi.com`, `www.caseycapozzi.com`
